# Product catalog

This widget can be used for provisioning of Virtual Machines (VM). The customised wizard helps to do that very quickly.
User can choose from several prepared products - as from plain operation systems (Windows or RHET) or web servers containing applications e.g. databases.  
<p>
<img src=" data:image/png;base64,"/>
</p>

## Wizzard running

Prepared wizard is designed for easy step-by-step going through. There are following steps:

 - "General" with Product name, Quantity, Environment, Location, Network Segment
 - "Availability settings" - for selection whether the machine is to be placed in an availability set, availability zone or stay unassigned 
 - "SW configuration" - application configuration
 - "VM configuration" - define virtual machine size
 - "GSN"


Notice:
If data in wizard are not valid for given configuration or user has to fill in missing information, then button "Next" is disabled until changes are made.

## Instalation

Some data are required and have to be corretly saved in external sources:

### List of countries
 - this list is saved in Secret Store Management under key "countries"
 - type of access is "Global resource"
 - format is JSON
 - example of data:
    
```json

{
    "United Arab Emirates": {
        "country_code": "AE",
        "region_code": "ASIA",
        "region_name": "ASIA"
    },
    "Syrian Arab Republic": {
        "country_code": "SY",
        "region_code": "ASIA",
        "region_name": "ASIA"
    },
    "Philippines": {
        "country_code": "PH",
        "region_code": "ASIA",
        "region_name": "ASIA"
    }
}
```

### GSN data
 - this JSON data is stored in folder

 - example of data:
```json
 {"result":
    [
        {"u_number":"BS25713","name":"BPM EGAP CBJ PROD"},
        {"u_number":"BS03943","name":"TKX CBJ SUPPORT"},
    ]
 }
```

### Default values
 - this default data for wizard is saved in Secret Store Management under key "defaults"
 - type of access is "tenant resource"
 - example of data:

```json
{
    "order_number":"001",
    "confidentiality": "for_internal_use",
    "business_unit":"Aviation",
    "business_service":"BS38866",
    "impact":"DEPARTMENT",
    "impacted_country":["Czechia","Algeria","Albania"],
    "impacted_region":["EUROPE","AFRICA"]
}

```
